<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .detail-box { background: white; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; }
        .detail-item { margin: 10px 0; font-size: 15px; }
        .label { font-weight: bold; color: #dc3545; }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>❌ Reservation Cancelled</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{ userName }}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Your reservation has been cancelled.</p>

            <div class="detail-box">
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="label">Voyage:</span> {{ voyageTitle }}
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>If you did not request this cancellation, please contact us immediately.</p>
            <p>You can always make a new reservation from our platform.</p>
            <p>— The Travigir Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply directly to this message.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>